Ian Smith winner of 2017 Walmer Park Kitchen Maestro Picture: Louise Liebenberg Ian Smith, of Kamma Park, claimed the 2017 Walmer Park Kitchen Maestro title at the final cook-off of the closely contested competition held in association with Weekend Post. Ian blew the judges away today SUN with his winning dish of pan-fried lamb loin chops with a coriander, turmeric and cumin rub, served with tender-stem broccoli, baby carrots and roasted vine tomatoes, and a mint, garlic, cucumber and yoghurt dipping sauce on the side. Helena Roux of Colchester took second place in the competition that boasted more than R50 000 in prize money this year Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share